                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18401019-2592-offence-1 t18401019-cd-179"></join>25th of September</rs>, 3 yards of printed-calico, value 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18401019-name-958" type="victimName">
